<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Notebook Entry</div>
<dl id="n01076m"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n01" href="#n01076m">N01 (VI.B.10)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n01all.htm#n01076m"> 76(m)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> Pierrepoint (boia) / invented strap ~</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources"><font color="green">[EXECUTIONER&apos;S DEATH]</font> Henry Albert <mark>Pierrepoint</mark>, for 11 years chief <mark>public executioner</mark> of England <font color="green">[&hellip;]</font> died yesterday morning at his home <font color="green">[&hellip;]</font> <font color="green">[F]</font>ollowing the hanging of a one-armed man in 1908 he <mark>invented a strap</mark> that has since been used for the pinioning of one-armed persons condemned to capitol punishment. <small> <a name="DM15dec22" href="../../ff/fdra/fdex.htm#DM15dec22"><cite title="source">Daily Mail</cite></a> (15 December 1922) 7/2</small></blockquote> <mm class="note">Note: Italian: <i>boia</i>, hangman. <br>Raphael transcription: <a name="c05140g" href="c05all.htm#c05140g">VI.C.05:140(g)</a> </mm></dd> </dd></dl>
